to amplify his power,

01:18:37.780 --> 01:18:41.082
a bargain will mean
an entity, influence,

01:18:48.124 --> 01:18:49.590
a wider result.

01:18:52.562 --> 01:18:57.264
- It sounds like it
already has a deal in mind.

